Package: bestsubset
Title: Best Subset Selection via MIQP with Validation Set Auto-Selection
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Edoardo", "Lanzetti", , "edoardo.lanzetti@epfl.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements an exact algorithm for Best Subset Selection in linear 
    regression using Mixed-Integer Quadratic Programming (MIQP) via the 'Gurobi' 
    optimizer. Features include warm-start optimization for sequential fitting, 
    Big-M constraint handling, and automatic model selection via validation set MSE.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
